<html>
  <head>
    <title>Verify Your Email Address - Shopwise</title>
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; background-color:
      #f5f5f5; } .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;
      background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 5px; box-shadow: 0 2px 5px
      rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); } .header { text-align: center; background-color:
      #f3f3f3; padding: 10px; border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0; } .header h1 { color:
      #333333; margin: 0; padding: 0; } .content { padding: 20px; } .footer {
      text-align: center; background-color: #f3f3f3; padding: 10px;
      border-radius: 0 0 5px 5px; } .footer p { margin: 0; padding: 0; } .button
      { display: inline-block; padding: 10px 20px; text-decoration: none; color:
      #ffffff; background-color: #3498db; border-radius: 5px; } .button:hover {
      background-color: #2980b9; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>Verify Your Email Address</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <p>Hello, {{name}}</p>
        <p>Thank you for signing up with Shopwise. To complete your
          registration, please verify your email address by clicking the button
          below:</p>
        <p>
          <a
            href="{{link}}"
            class="button"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >Verify Email</a>
        </p>
        <p>If the button above is not working, you can also copy and paste the
          following link into your browser:</p>
        <p>
          <a
            href="{{link}}"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >{{link}}</a>
        </p>
        <p>If you did not sign up for an account on Shopwise, you can ignore
          this email.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <p>Best regards,<br />Shopwise Team</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>